messages.text: hey john! i was wondering if you were around at all today?
hey neighbor, i’m almost at my apartment – what’s up?
this is a little embarrassing, but my toilet is super clogged
would you be able to come next door for a bit and help me unclog it?
don’t you have a plunger?
ugh no, they gross me out too much to keep one around
lol, i see
that’s okay, i have one. i’ll be over in a few
thanks sooo much!! you are amazing
3 Days Later
hey john! sorry to be such a pain, but are you around?
hey marina, what’s up?
my garbage disposal thingy in the sink is jammed or something
i can’t seem to get it working
would you be willing to help me out?
hmmm
i ordered some pizza
why didn’t you lead with that
be right there
yay! it’s almost here so hurry up
3 Days Later
hey john
i’m sure you would never be able to guess this but
i need your help again
hahah what is it now?
i ordered this bed from ikea and…well…
say no more
i am at your service
yay!! thank god
i can come over around 8?
yes please
you’re a lifesaver
and much more handsome than the guy at ikea customer service
why thank you
how did you get so good at this stuff anyway?
well my dad built houses for a living
and i’m actually a furniture maker by trade
what?! that’s so cool! i had no idea!
anyway, i guess i’m just used to building and making stuff
i like fixing things for people
that’s really great, john
sounds very manly
it’s the manliest
well i really appreciate the help, mr. man
it’s my pleasure
anyway see you tonight
the pleasure is all mine. yes see you tonight!
4 Days Later
hey there
hey there stranger! how are you?
good good
just wanted to check in and see how everything i fixed is doing
see if you needed any extra help or anything
everything is working perfectly now thanks to you
oh, cool
glad i was able to help
actually…
i mean, there’s this light bulb that went out in my bathroom
and i can’t reach it to change it
and since you’re pretty tall and all
i’m guessing you don’t own a step stool?
or any chairs you could stand on to fix it?
something like that
haha alright, be right there
hurry up! i can’t see anything in this pitch darkness!
thought you said it was just one light bulb
i may have unscrewed a few more by accident
what a happy accident
well come on! hurry up and get here already!
i’m at the door, let me in silly
3 Days Later
that lasagna we ate the other night once we finally found those bulbs you hid was incredible. mind sending over the recipe?
i have no idea what you’re talking about…and hold up, you cook?
of course
that’s a great trait, you know
very desirable in a man
so i’ve been told
so wait, be real with me. how are you single?! you’re such a great guy
idk, it’s one of the great mysteries of the universe
anyway, i can’t pass on the recipe because it’s a family secret!
really?
we guard it with our lives and pass it down from generation to generation
very fancy
nah i’m just kidding, it’s just the frozen kind
i can check the box for the brand and let you know
really? you’re not committing blasphemy as a chef by eating frozen food?
even i occasionally must give in to temptation…and hot pockets
nobody blames you at all
you know, i can just come over and check the brand
and in the process, maybe i could cook dinner for you this time
oh, that’s really sweet john
could we do it another night? i’m sort of busy tonight
oh yeah, of course! what are you up to?
my boyfriend is back from his business trip and i’m taking him out to celebrate
oh
ok
gotcha
well have a great night
thank you!! we will!
4 Days Later
hey john, i can’t figure out how to get my kitchen drawer open. it’s completely stuck. you around?
hey, no, sorry
well are you able to come over later tonight at all and take a look?
nope, super busy
oh what, you got a hot date?
idk
would it matter to you if i did?
of course not
maybe just a little bit
marina…you need to stop texting me and get your boyfriend to fix it
but he’s at work right now
and that’s my problem how
why are you being like this?
i felt like we were getting along really well
you just weren’t very up front with me about things
and you had tons of opportunities to mention him
look, he’s always working, we barely talk anymore
i spend more time with you
and it’s been so nice having a guy around who can take care of stuff
i’m sorry you’re not happy in your relationship
but it doesn’t mean you get to string me along on the side
i never meant to do that
and who are you to judge and say i’m not happy?
marina… be honest with yourself
you found excuses to hang out with me
it’s clear you feel like something is missing
so now you’re a therapist or something?
i never made you any promises
i never flirted with you, and i didn’t intentionally lead you on
come on, marina
calling me handsome, calling me manly and desirable
you unscrewed light bulbs just so that you could have me come over
you flirted.
i thought we were friends, so sue me
we’re not friends
we’re neighbors who only sort of know each other but who have been having romantic dinners together for weeks now
most of which, you cooked for me
romantic?! you think i cooked for you?!
we both know you made that lasagna from scratch
so what if i did
sooo sorry i went out of my way to do something nice for you
amazing! turns out we feel the same way
for the record, those things were actually broken
and you’re cheaper than a plumber or electrician
well i’m glad you feel you got what you needed out of me
come on…i didn’t mean to say it like that
i think you did
i think we are better off just being neighbors
so don’t contact me again unless the building is burning down
hold on
john just wait
what if i was to break up with my boyfriend?
would that make a difference?
marina…
i’m the guy who fixes things, remember? not the one who breaks them
….ok
i see your point
i’m sorry about all of this, john
i’ll leave you alone now
but i just want you to know
you are a really really great guy
yup. so i’ve been told.
